        <!-- Q1 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    证明等比级数 (几何级数)  <m> \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a q^{n-1}(a \neq 0) </m> 收敛的充要条件是  <m> |q| \lt 1 </m> , 并求其和  <m> s </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证 当  <m> q \neq 1 </m>  时, 部分和
                    <me> 
                    s_{n}=a\left(1+q+q^{2}+\cdots+q^{n-1}\right)=\frac{a\left(1-q^{n}\right)}{1-q}, n=1,2, \cdots .
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 于是  <m> \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} s_{n}=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{a\left(1-q^{n}\right)}{1-q}=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}\frac{a}{1-q},  &amp;  |q| \lt 1, \\ \infty,  &amp;  |q| \gt 1 ;\end{array}\right. </m> 
                    当  <m> q=-1 </m>  时,  <m> s_{2 n-1}=a(a \neq 0), s_{2 n}=0 </m> , 于是  <m> \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} s_{n} </m>  不存在；
                    当  <m> q=1 </m>  时,  <m> s_{n}=n a(a \neq 0) </m> ,于是  <m> \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} s_{n}=\infty </m> . </p> 

                    <p> 所以, 当且仅当  <m> |q| \lt 1 </m>  时  <m> \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a q^{n-1} </m>  收敛, 此时  <m> \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a q^{n-1}=\frac{a}{1-q} </m>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    证明  <m> p- </m>  级数  <m> \displaystyle\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{p}} </m>  仅当  <m> p \gt 1 </m>  时收敛.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    证 当  <m> p \leq 0 </m>  时,  <m> \because \lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n^{p}} \neq 0 </m> ,  <m> \therefore p  </m> -级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{p}} </m>  发散. 下设  <m> p \gt 0 </m> .
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    \because \int_{1}^{+\infty} \frac{1}{x^{p}} \mathrm{~d} x  &amp;  =\left\{\begin{array}{ll}
                    \left.\frac{1}{1-p} x^{1-p}\right|_{1} ^{+\infty},  &amp;  p \neq 1, \\
                    \left.\ln x\right|_{1} ^{+\infty},  &amp;  p=1
                    \end{array}\right. \\
                    &amp;  =\left\{\begin{array}{ll}
                    \frac{1}{p-1},  &amp;  p \gt 1, \\
                    +\infty,  &amp;  p \leq 1 .
                    \end{array}\right.
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p>  <m> \therefore p </m> -级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{p}}  </m>  当  <m>  p \gt 1  </m>  时收敛,当  <m>  p \leq 1 </m>  时发散.
                    由此可知  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{2}}, \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{\frac{3}{2}}} </m>  等都收敛, 而  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n} </m>  (调和级数),  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} </m>  等都发散.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    证明级数  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n(n+1)} </m>  收敛, 并求其和.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解1: 
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    \because s_{n} &amp; =\sum_{k=1}^{n} \frac{1}{k(k+1)}=\sum_{k=1}^{n}\left(\frac{1}{k}-\frac{1}{k+1}\right)\\
                    &amp; =\left(1-\frac{1}{2}\right)+\left(\frac{1}{2}-\frac{1}{3}\right)+\left(\frac{1}{3}-\frac{1}{4}\right)+\cdots+\left(\frac{1}{n-1}-\frac{1}{n}\right)+\left(\frac{1}{n}-\frac{1}{n+1}\right) \\
                    &amp; =1-\frac{1}{n+1} \rightarrow 1(n \rightarrow \infty),
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p>  <m> \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n(n+1)} </m> ,  且   <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n(n+1)}=1 </m>  . </p> 

                    <p> 解2: 令  <m> u_{n}=\frac{1}{n(n+1)} </m> , 设  <m> v_{n}=\frac{1}{n^{2}} </m> ,  <m> \because \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{u_{n}}{v_{n}}=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{n^{2}}{n(n+1)}=1 </m> ,  <m> 0 \lt 1 \lt +\infty </m> ,
                    由比较判别法的极限形式得,  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n} </m>  与  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} v_{n}  </m>  同敛散。
                    <m> \because \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} v_{n}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{2}} </m>  中  <m> p=2 \gt 1 </m> , 所以收敛, 即原级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n(n+1)} </m>  收敛.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

