        <!-- Q5 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{2^{n}+3^{n}}{6^{n}} </m>  敛散性的正确结论为( ) 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <choices>
                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            发散
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
                
                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            收敛且和为  <m> 2 </m> 
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            收敛且和为  <m> 1 </m> 
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice correct="yes">
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            收敛且和为  <m> \frac{3}{2} </m>
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
            
            </choices>
            
			<answer>
                	<p>
                        解:  <m> \because \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{2^{n}+3^{n}}{6^{n}}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n}+\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^{n} </m> , 且  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n} </m>  和  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^{n} </m>  为 公比  <m> q(|q| \lt 1) </m>  的等比级数,由级数的性质 2 知,  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{2^{n}+3^{n}}{6^{n}} </m>  收敛, 且  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n}=\frac{\frac{1}{3}}{1-\frac{1}{3}}=\frac{1}{2}, \quad \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^{n}=\frac{\frac{1}{2}}{1-\frac{1}{2}}=1 </m> ,故  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{2^{n}+3^{n}}{6^{n}}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n}+\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{1}{2}\right)^{n}=\frac{3}{2} </m>
                	</p>
          	</answer>
		</exercise>


        <!-- Q6 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    已知  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n-1} a_{n}=2 </m> ,  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n-1}=5 </m> , 则  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{n}= </m> ________.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 因为  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{n}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(a_{2 n-1}+a_{2 n}\right)=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n-1}+\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n} </m>  故关键是求出  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n} </m> .
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    \text { 而 } \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n}  &amp;  =\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\left[a_{2 n-1}-(-1)^{n-1} a_{n}\right]=\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{2 n-1}-\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n-1} a_{n} \\
                    &amp;  =5-2=3, \\
                    \therefore \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} a_{n} &amp; =5+3  =8 .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q7 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    判定级数  <m> \frac{1}{\sqrt{2}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}+1}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}+1}+\cdots+\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}+1}+\cdots </m>  敛散性.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 对原级数加括号得
                    <me> 
                    \left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{2}+1}\right)+\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{3}+1}\right)+\cdots+\left(\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}+1}\right)+\cdots
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 通项  <m> u_{n}=\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}-1}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{n}+1}=\frac{2}{n-1} </m> , 而级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty} \frac{2}{n-1}=2 \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n} </m>  发散, 即加括号后所得级数发散,故原级数必发散. </p> 

                    <p> 用级数的性质可判断添加括号后级数的敛散性. 若级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n}, \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} v_{n} </m>  均收敛,则  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(u_{n}+v_{n}\right) </m>  收敛; 若  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n}, \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} v_{n} </m>  中一个收敛,一个发散, 则  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(u_{n}+v_{n}\right) </m>  发散; 若  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} u_{n}, \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} v_{n} </m>  均发散,则  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(u_{n}+v_{n}\right) </m>  敛散性不确定. 级数添加括号后得到的级数发散, 则原级数必发散, 但是添加括号后得到的级数收敛, 并不能判定出原级数的敛散性.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q8 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    判定下列级数的敛散性: </p> 

                    <p> (1)  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\left[\sqrt{2}+(-1)^{n}\right]^{n}}{3^{n}} </m> ;
                    (2)  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \int_{n}^{n+1} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{x} \mathrm{~d} x </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解(1)  <m> \because \frac{\left[\sqrt{2}+(-1)^{n}\right]^{n}}{3^{n}} \leq \frac{[\sqrt{2}+1]^{n}}{3^{n}} </m> ,
                    而  <m> \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \sqrt[n]{\frac{[\sqrt{2}+1]^{n}}{3^{n}}}=\frac{\sqrt{2}+1}{3} \lt 1 </m> ,
                    于是  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{[\sqrt{2}+1]^{n}}{3^{n}}  </m>  收敛, 所以原级数收敛. </p> 

                    <p> (2)  <m> \because \int_{n}^{n+1} \frac{\mathrm{e}^{-x}}{x} \mathrm{~d} x \leq \int_{n}^{n+1} \mathrm{e}^{-x} \mathrm{~d} x </m> , 
                    <m> \int_{n}^{n+1} \mathrm{e}^{-x} \mathrm{~d} x=-\left.\mathrm{e}^{-x}\right|_{n} ^{n+1}=\frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^{n}}-\frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^{n+1}}=\left(1-\mathrm{e}^{-1}\right) \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^{n}} </m>  </p> 

                    <p> 而  <m>  \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{\mathrm{e}^{n}}  </m>  收敛, 所以原级数收敛.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    判定  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{1+\frac 1n}}, \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\ln n}{n^{2}}, \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{\sqrt{n(n+1)}}  </m>  的敛散性.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解 (1)  <m> \because \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\frac{1}{n^{1+\frac{1}{n}}}}{\frac{1}{n}}=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{n^{\frac{1}{n}}}=1 </m> , 而  <m> \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n} </m>  发散,  <m> \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{1+\frac{1}{n}}} </m>  发散. </p> 

                    <p> (2)  <m> \because \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\frac{\ln n}{n^{2}}}{\frac{1}{n^{\frac{3}{2}}}}=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\ln n}{\sqrt{n}}=0 </m> , 而  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n^{\frac{3}{2}}} </m>  收敛,  <m>  \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{\ln n}{n^{2}} </m>  收敛.
                    (3)  <m> \because \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\frac{1}{\sqrt{n(n+1)}}}{\frac{1}{n}}=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{n}{\sqrt{n(n+1)}}=1 </m> , 由于  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{n} </m>  发散,  <m> \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{\sqrt{n(n+1)}} </m>  发散.
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q10 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    判定下列级数的敛散性.
                    (1)  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} n \tan \frac{\pi}{2^{n+1}} </m> 
                    (2)  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \sqrt{n}[\ln (1+n)-\ln n] </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: (1)  <m> \because n \rightarrow \infty </m>  时  <m> n \tan \frac{\pi}{2^{n+1}}\sim \frac{\pi}{2} \frac{n}{2^{n}} </m>  而  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{n}{2^{n}} </m>  收敛,
                    <m> \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} n \tan \frac{\pi}{2^{n+1}} </m>  收敛.
                    (2)  <m> \because n \rightarrow \infty </m>  时  <m> \sqrt{n}[\ln (1+n)-\ln n]=\sqrt{n}\left[\ln \left(\frac{1+n}{n}\right)\right] \sim \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} </m> ,
                    而  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1}{\sqrt{n}} </m>  发散，  <m> \therefore \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \sqrt{n}[\ln (1+n)-\ln n] </m>  发散. 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

