        <!-- Q12 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    判定级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}} </m>  的敛散性.
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解法一: 已给的正项级数的通项为  <m> u_{n}=\frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}} </m> , 取正项的等比级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n} </m>  的通项  <m> v_{n}=\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n} </m>  与之比较, 则有
                    <me> 
                    \lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{u_{n}}{v_{n}}=\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{\frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}}}{\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n}}=\lim _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{7^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}}=1 .
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 由定理 3 可知,  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}} </m>  与  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n} </m>  具有相同的散性, 而  <m>  \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n}  </m>  是收敛的等比级数, 故知级数  <m> \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}} </m>  收敛.
                    解法二 所给的级数为通项为  <m>  u_{n}  </m>  的正项级数, 且
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    u_{n}  &amp;  =\frac{6^{n}}{7^{n}-5^{n}}=\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n} \frac{1}{\left[1-\left(\frac{5}{7}\right)^{n}\right]} \leqslant\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n} \frac{1}{1-\frac{5}{7}} \\
                    &amp;  =\frac{7}{2}\left(\frac{6}{7}\right)^{n}=v_{n} .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

