                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解   <m> \because \lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty}\left|\frac{u_{n+1}(x)}{u_{n}(x)}\right|=\lim\limits _{n \rightarrow \infty} \frac{n(2 n+1)}{(n+1)(2 n+3)} x^{2}=x^{2} </m> ,  <m> \therefore  </m>  当  <m> x^{2} \lt 1 </m> 
                    即  <m> |x| \lt 1 </m>  时幂级数绝对收玫, 当  <m> x^{2} \gt 1 </m>  即  <m> |x| \gt 1 </m>  时发散, 故  <m> R=1 </m> ; 又当  <m> x= \pm 1 </m>  时级数收玫所以  <m> D=[-1,1] </m> .
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    \text { 令 } s(x) &amp; =\sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n-1} x^{2 n}}{n(2 n-1)}, x \in[-1,1] \text {, 则 } s(0)=0 . \\
                    \because s^{\prime}(x) &amp; =2 \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n-1} x^{2 n-1}}{2 n-1}, x \in[-1,1] \text {, 且 } s^{\prime}(0)=0 ; \\
                    s^{\prime \prime}(x) &amp; =2 \sum_{n=1}^{\infty}(-1)^{n-1} x^{2 n-2}=2 \cdot \frac{1}{1+x^{2}}=\frac{2}{1+x^{2}}, x \in(-1,1) ; \\
                    \therefore s^{\prime}(x) &amp; =s^{\prime}(0)+\int_{0}^{x} s^{\prime \prime}(x) \mathrm{d} x=2 \int_{0}^{x} \frac{1}{1+x^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x=2 \arctan x, x \in[-1,1] ; \\
                    \text { 故 } s(x) &amp; =s(0)+\int_{0}^{x} s^{\prime}(x) \mathrm{d} x=\int_{0}^{x} 2 \arctan x \mathrm{~d} x=2 x \arctan x-\int_{0}^{x} \frac{2 x}{1+x^{2}} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                    &amp; =2 \arctan x-\ln \left(1+x^{2}\right), x \in[-1,1] . \\
                    \text { 即 } \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{(-1)^{n-1} x^{2 n}}{n(2 n-1)} &amp; =2 \arctan x-\ln \left(1+x^{2}\right), x \in[-1,1] .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

