                    解 因  <m> f(x) </m>  只在半区间  <m> [0,2] </m>  上给出, 故需将其延拓成  <m> [-2,2] </m>  上的偶函数. 此时所展余弦级数的周期为  <m> 4(l=2) </m> .
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    b_{n}  &amp;  =0, n \in \mathbf{Z}^{+} \\
                    a_{0}  &amp;  =\frac{2}{2} \int_{0}^{2} f(x) \mathrm{d} x=\int_{0}^{1}(1-x) \mathrm{d} x=\frac{1}{2}, \\
                    a_{n}  &amp;  =\frac{2}{2} \int_{0}^{2} f(x) \cos \frac{n \pi x}{2} \mathrm{~d} x=\int_{0}^{1}(1-x) \cos \frac{n \pi x}{2} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                    &amp;  =\left[(1-x) \frac{2}{n \pi} \sin \frac{n \pi x}{2}\right]_{0}^{1}+\frac{2}{n \pi} \int_{0}^{1} \sin \frac{n \pi x}{2} \mathrm{~d} x \\
                    &amp;  =-\left.\frac{4}{n^{2} \pi^{2}} \cos \frac{n \pi x}{2}\right|_{0} ^{1}=\frac{4}{n^{2} \pi^{2}}\left(1-\cos \frac{n \pi}{2}\right), n \in \mathbf{Z}^{+} ;
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 即   <m> a_{n}=\frac{4}{n^{2} \pi^{2}}\left(1-\cos \frac{n \pi}{2}\right)=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}\frac{4}{n^{2} \pi^{2}},  &amp;  n=1,3,5,7, \cdots, \\ \frac{8}{n^{2} \pi^{2}},  &amp;  n=2,6,10, \cdots, \\ 0,  &amp;  n=4,8,12, \cdots\end{array}\right. </m>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me> \begin{aligned} \therefore f(x) &amp; =\frac{1}{4}+\frac{4}{\pi^{2}} \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \frac{1-\cos \frac{n \pi}{2}}{n^{2}} \cos \frac{n \pi}{2} x \\  &amp; =\frac{1}{4}+\frac{4}{\pi^{2}}\left(\frac{1}{1^{2}} \cos \frac{\pi x}{2}+\frac{2}{2^{2}} \cos \frac{2 \pi x}{2}+\frac{1}{3^{2}} \cos \frac{3 \pi x}{2}+\frac{1}{5^{2}} \cos \frac{5 \pi x}{2}\right. \\  &amp; \left.\quad+\frac{2}{6^{2}} \cos \frac{6 \pi x}{2}+\frac{1}{7^{2}} \cos \frac{7 \pi x}{2}+\frac{1}{9^{2}} \cos \frac{9 \pi x}{2}+\cdots\right) .\end{aligned} </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
